# ðŸ”— GoLink - Professional URL Shortener

A full-stack URL shortener application built with Go and React that allows you to create shortened links with click tracking and analytics.

## Live Demo

- **Frontend**: [https://url-shortener-khaki-five.vercel.app](https://url-shortener-khaki-five.vercel.app)
- **Backend API**: [https://urlshortner-production-fbd3.up.railway.app](https://urlshortner-production-fbd3.up.railway.app)
## Live Link to Video
https://urlshortner-production-fbd3.up.railway.app/St8pvV OR https://drive.google.com/file/d/1H_YCjM7C0ybhNLeOoPQlS2g1cAXI-0Sx/view?usp=drive_link
##  Features

- **Shorten URLs** - Convert long URLs into short, shareable links
- **Click Tracking** - Track how many times each short link has been clicked
- **Lookup Stats** - Check statistics for existing short codes
- **Persistent Storage** - Data survives server restarts via file-based storage
-  **Modern UI** - Clean, responsive interface built with React and Tailwind CSS
-  **Fast Redirects** - Instant redirection to original URLs
- **Thread-Safe** - Handles concurrent requests safely with mutex locks

##  Tech Stack

### Backend
- **Go 1.22+** - High-performance backend server
- **Gorilla Mux** - HTTP router and URL matcher
- **CORS** - Cross-Origin Resource Sharing support
- **JSON Storage** - File-based persistence

### Frontend
- **React 18** - Modern UI library
- **Axios** - HTTP client for API requests
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first CSS framework
- **Create React App** - Build tooling

### Deployment
- **Railway** - Backend hosting
- **Vercel** - Frontend hosting

